title: Belladonna: Fire & Fury
description: The Redhead Raider is back in a huge new Viking epic as Belladonna unleashes Fire & Fury!

title: Mask Omnibus
description: It has all the makings of an epic adventure: an ancient artifact is rediscovered; a mask of unknown origins, with unforeseen power and magic.

title: Star Wars: Crimson Empire
description: Kir Kanos is the last surviving member of the elite Imperial Guard. He's on the run -- and the Empire will stop at nothing to destroy him!

title: Buffy the Vampire Slayer

title: Aliens: The Original Years
description: As Marvel prepares for a xenomorph invasion, rediscover the comic book legacy of ALIENS!
